profile:
At Long Life, we specialize in three things: replacement windows, replacement doors, and exceptional installation service.


Our team includes the best replacement window installers in the Lower Mainland, with years of experience in the industry, the latest tools, and pride in our work. From fabricating custom replacement window trims, to making friends with the family pet, our installation professionals have the exceptional service attitude that has built our business.


So it only makes sense for us to install the best products available. Our locally made replacement windows and doors are renowned for quality, innovation, and lifetime warranty service.Our hands-on approach ensures we deliver what we promise. And it’s why word of mouth advertising is the biggest builder of our business. 


Our Replacement Windows: We install many kinds of vinyl windows: sliders, crank casement windows, push out casement windows, and tilt and turn windows. You can select optional grids, colours, and window configurations to fit with your home’s current style, or to create a new one.


Our Replacement Doors: We install sliding patio doors, and all kinds of custom entry doors: steel, fiberglass, wood and vinyl. With our extensive options, you can design the door you want.


Getting new windows and replacement doors is easy when you’re working with Long Life, a family-run company with a reputation that speaks for itself. With no subcontracting, no deposits, and lifelong warranties, you’ll always have peace of mind.

profile: We specialize in replacement windows, doors and patio doors for the residential market and work directly with homeowners, and take care of supplying and installing the windows and doors. We offer energy efficient vinyl windows, steel and fibreglass doors and patio doors. Our window options include casement, awning, slider, hung, bay, bow, shape and combination windows. Our windows and doors available with triple-pane glass on all our models including slider and hung windows. We offer financing options, and have our own dedicated installers. After the installation we dispose of your old windows and doors. All our windows and doors come with product and installation warranty. Our mission is to improve your home!

profile:
For over 30 years A1 Windows has been manufacturing and installing windows for all type of homes; from single family to high rise.

Whether aluminium or vinyl, our West Coast designed and built windows and patio doors not only meet but exceed local and national standards for energy performance.

Our aim is to provide you with the very best value in windows and patio doors by combining quality products, award-winning service and everyday competitive pricing.

A1 Windows has experience working in various market segments including:

    * Residential Single Family Window Replacement
    * High-Rise and Mid-Rise Window Replacement (condo/co-op/office)
    * Apartment and Penthouse Window Replacement
    * Strata and Depreciation Reports requiring Window Replacement
    * Garden Apartment and Multi-Family Window Replacement
    * Office and Industrial Window Replacement
    * School and Church Window Replacement
    * Hospitality and Hotel Window Replacement
    * Senior and Assisted Living Window Replacement
    * Custom Home and Residential Window Replacement

While most of our projects take place in the Lower Mainland of BC, we are capable of supply-only contracts to fulfil throughout Canada and the USA.

Our direct service areas include: Abbotsford, Albion, Anmore, Annieville, Barnston Island, Belcarra, Boundary Bay, Bridgeport, Brighouse, Burnaby, Burquitlam, Cloverdale, Coquitlam, Crescent Beach, Delta, Fort Langley, Haney, Langley City, Langley District, Maillardville, Maple Ridge, Mission, New Westminster, Newton, North Vancouver City, North Vancouver District, Pitt Meadows, Port Coquitlam, Port Kells, Port Moody, Queensborough, Richmond, Sapperton, Steveston, Surrey, Tsawwassen, Vancouver, West Vancouver, Whalley, White Rock

How to get a Free Quote: call 604-777-8000 or email info@a1windows.ca

profile: Our team of skilled craftsmen can help you with a wide range of exterior renovations including installing new windows and doors, siding and soffit, painting and staining, and heritage restoration. From patio and garden structures to building deck, stairs, and railings, let us create your dream outdoor living space. MASTER SOLUTION will carry your renovation visions to life with more than 10 years of exterior renovation experience in Vancouver and the Lower Mainland. Our expertise is an outstanding renovation process.
products:
Proudly serving the Lower Mainland since 2007, we are a dedicated team of skilled craftsmen with over 15 years of experience in specialized maintenance & installations, remodeling (shelves, storage, decks), carpentry, drywall, and painting. We offer affordable services in Vancouver, Burnaby, North Vancouver, West Vancouver, New Westminster, and other areas for residents and businesses. We customize our service to each of your individual needs and provide excellent customer service with reliable, guaranteed workmanship. We are licensed, and we carry $2,000,000.00 liability insurance.

We bring consistency from construction, design, and decoration from the start of your project to completion, providing you with a unique and innovative style in the market.

profile: Ecowest Renovations provides all the services you need to create a more comfortable, energy-efficient home, including vinyl replacement windows, entrance doors, vinyl siding, furnaces, heat pumps and more. We also specialize in bathrooms, additions, decks, and other types of renovations. Beginning with an in-home consultation, our goal is to make the process as seamless and trouble-free as possible for you.
hours: Showroom: Mon-Fri 8:30-4:30, Sat 10-4, Sun by appointment
products: Westeck and Jeld-Wen , Valor fireplaces, doors, insulation, ventilation, siding, roofing, heating, furnaces, floors, bathrooms, decks, additions.
services: Financing of up to 50K through TD Financing services. We also fully project manage all our work from the time of purchase to project completion.
brands: We carry many major brands including Westeck and Jeld-Wen windows and doors, Valor Fireplaces, American Standard Heating Products,  Panasonic ventilation systems, Weiser, Masonite, Mitten Siding, Owens Corning, Specialty Glass, Trimlite and more.
specialities: Energy efficient products and services, custom fireplaces, medium to high-end bathroom and kitchen renovations.
payment_method: TD Home Improvement Financing (approval can be completed at our office in about 5 minutes), Visa, MasterCard, and cheques.
licenses: Ecowest is a Registered Gas Contractor.
memberships: GVHBA, CHBA, Renomark, Chambers of Commerce, BBB, Vancouver Board of Trade.
project_rate: Each project is detailed on an itemized estimate.
warranty_terms: Lifetime Warranty on most window and door installations, minimum 5 years on all other types of renov
name: Ecowest Renovations-No Longer in Business
